The paper deals with domain adaptation, which is a common problem in machine learning, and proposes a new method to improve the robustness of existing methods against mismatched label distributions. The paper also provides theoretical guarantees and modifies existing algorithms. Given these factors, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
